data.description: PRIVACY & LOCATION! Updated Ranch on over 2 acres in Cherokee County! No HOA. Conveniently located near Hwy 20, 575 and only 2.5 miles from Allatoona Lake and FieldCOs Landing Park with boat ramp, fishing dock, playground, picnic areas and pavilions. This home features a spacious family room with wood burning stove open to the kitchen with granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and stained cabinets. The primary bedroom features an in-suite bath with granite counter and shower/tub combo. There are also two secondary bedrooms and an additional full bath with granite counter. Brand new well! Large rocking chair front porch and outdoor firepit area are perfect for entertaining or relaxing. Ample sized carport with storage room and additional huge crawl space area with garage door provides plenty of space for cars, tools and toys!
